Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.67,0:01:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.27,0:01:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟之国的任务已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.07,0:01:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.47,0:01:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样的话 鸣人怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.97,0:01:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是我这个队长的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.67,0:02:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者的任务往往伴随牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.77,0:02:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 回村吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.97,0:02:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为他们真的会回去吗 流
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.47,0:02:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是比较在意那个带面罩的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我去跟踪他们吗 北辰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.97,0:02:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 还是我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.37,0:02:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回去汇报一下情况
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人之死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.57,0:03:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余下二人以及后来赶来汇合的一个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.57,0:03:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经出了国境
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.47,0:03:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该在回木叶村的路上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.37,0:03:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜入大名府的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像已经被鹭大人处决了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好茶好茶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这帮家伙从刚才开始到底在干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.17,0:03:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是柿子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干吗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.57,0:03:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:03:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替身术
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木叶的忍者们居然敢欺骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红明大人 请出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟之国 谋士红明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滥用国家谋士之权
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗杀前代大名以及公主朱鹭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且派遣部下装扮成诅咒武士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专横跋扈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛊惑人心 干涉朝政
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此等危及鹭大人大名之位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.27,0:05:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篡位害人之罪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.07,0:05:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天地难容
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.97,0:06:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 赐你切腹自刎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此啊 是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,申子绪 你居然陷害我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丢脸啊 红明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士就该有气魄以死谢罪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即执行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.37,0:07:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雾隐之术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.77,0:07:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管这些 赶快杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上路吧 对不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.07,0:07:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.17,0:07:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就是诅咒武士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们继续追
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先行一步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事需要调查
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:07:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.37,0:08:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们果然是一伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是那天晚上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵的真面目 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.37,0:08:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操纵诅咒武士的就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是为了调查诅咒武士而去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那位大人会这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不见棺材不掉泪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我来揭穿你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:08:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.57,0:09:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您刚才到那儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下再解释吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们赶快离开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 你们也跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 天天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 宁次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直跟踪我们的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.57,0:09:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你不想出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.87,0:09:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通灵之术
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.97,0:09:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮忙找出隐藏在这里的忍者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小事一桩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:09:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 躲在这边的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:10:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉迷藏的游戏到此为止了 快出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.77,0:10:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗鼻子果然与众不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来躲不了了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.17,0:10:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总算肯现身了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里怎么会有这样的地道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.57,0:10:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说大名为了能了解庶民们的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而开凿了这条遍布全国范围的地道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.67,0:10:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说诅咒武士和大名有关咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少不会是幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.57,0:10:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在过会儿 对方应该会自表身份的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.77,0:11:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务结束后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返回村子应该是被雇佣忍者们的常识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务的初衷既然变了 那就另当别论了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的任务疑点太多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们过于干涉别国的内政了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.17,0:11:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不像狗一样乱闻的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来应该可以活着回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.07,0:11:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉 狗招你惹你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森罗万象 防护之术
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.77,0:11:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.67,0:11:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道身体里含有岩石的成份吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.97,0:11:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然已经知道这个国家的秘密了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能让你们活着回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像比较麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:11:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:11:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:12:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的我一个人能够应付
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.87,0:12:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 那我先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬化 岩石战车
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.27,0:12:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.97,0:12:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.27,0:12:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引爆符
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.27,0:12:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这里应该可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:12:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.67,0:13:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣…鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.87,0:13:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒武士的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是鹭大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…你到底是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鹭大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.47,0:13:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是鹭大人做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.27,0:14:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那个站姿来看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.27,0:14:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确定就是鹭大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.27,0:14:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实情况比较复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.27,0:14:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干吗啊 天天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么不早点告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.47,0:14:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有宁次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很早就知道是鸣人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.37,0:14:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么能这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.37,0:14:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可担心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一直有忍者在监视我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宁次 天天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加快步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们被人跟踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在返回鸟之国
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.67,0:14:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别被发现了 就现在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:14:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:15:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是用替身把那人甩了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.97,0:15:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可那只是暂时性的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.27,0:15:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刑场追诅咒武士开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个人又跟了上来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.07,0:15:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一个人知情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是白提你们操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是你代替鹭大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.87,0:15:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那鹭大人平安无事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.87,0:15:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们担心了 哪个可恶的申子绪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,严刑拷打逼我认罪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.17,0:15:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 你受了很多罪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.97,0:15:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来龙去脉 进去以后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.87,0:15:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹭大哥等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬化 岩吹雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们流浪忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.07,0:16:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有归属之地 四处辗转
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷学各村忍术精髓 创造属于自己的招式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说这招
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写轮眼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.47,0:16:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬化 砂缚枢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙 居然连我爱罗的忍术也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬化 砂瀑送葬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹭大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.87,0:16:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千岛大哥情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.77,0:16:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有生命危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.37,0:16:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在我府邸的医疗室接受治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:16:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在休息当中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千岛他怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.77,0:17:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁…是谁干的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.07,0:17:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,误会你了 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.37,0:17:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小人实在承受不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是千岛他拼了命前来告诉我实情的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.87,0:17:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今却不能让知道一切的你活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私闯大名府 你已经是死罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹭大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千岛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是飞镖所伤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.07,0:17:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快去御医那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.37,0:17:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹭大人 请听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:17:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,申子绪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 申子绪背叛了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗杀你父亲和妹妹的也是他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.17,0:18:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他指派自己的亲信忍者使用近卫兵的飞镖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.77,0:18:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的是嫁祸给红明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.77,0:18:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是被申子绪给暗算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撑住啊 千岛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹭大人 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.07,0:18:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快停止红明大人的处刑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.27,0:18:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不去就晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以停止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.77,0:18:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果让申子绪发现我已经知道真相了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就无法复仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.17,0:18:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你为了复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜牺牲任何人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我能如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红明被申子绪的心腹看守着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.27,0:18:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是贸然出手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们更本没有任何胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:18:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那让我去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人去救红明大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样你该没意见了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.97,0:19:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹭大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.57,0:19:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便你怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.37,0:19:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我就假扮了诅咒武士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己扮成诅咒武士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.87,0:19:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为的是寻找暗杀父亲的真凶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是非但没有找到凶手 红明…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.07,0:19:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而却成了陷害你的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.37,0:19:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直觉得那天的诅咒武士就是您
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才去了诅咒武士一度消失的寺庙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就遇到了诅咒武士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.07,0:20:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那个诅咒武士并不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是申子绪叫人伪装的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都明了了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是申子绪那个老头搞的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,申子绪这个老匹夫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道想先除了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再谋害鹭大人篡位吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个老头居然还假惺惺的装好人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.57,0:20:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想揍他一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人还有各位 辛苦你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.07,0:20:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在开始 一切都交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.37,0:20:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我一个人去了结吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:20:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心中的表
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然只会停留在过去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.57,0:22:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人能干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.29,0:22:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你想复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.31,0:22:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可人死不能复生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.50,0:22:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 你还执着于复仇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.11,0:22:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做能让你快乐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.50,0:22:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.90,0:23:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的父亲和妹妹真的会高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.46,0:23:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.27,0:23:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静止的时间